
Phase 1: Setup (Week 1-2)

1. Define properties in your project management tool
2. Document property usage guidelines
3. Train team leads on proper usage

Phase 2: Automation (Week 3-4)

1. Implement basic label-to-property mapping
2. Set up quarterly cleanup reminder
3. Create property usage dashboard

Phase 3: Optimization (Quarter 2+)

1. Add AI-powered suggestions
2. Implement property validation
3. Create automated reporting